Interface Vector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DenseVector, SparseVector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSafeVector, AbstractVector, BasicVector, CompressedVector, DenseSafeVector, SparseSafeVector

    public interface Vector
extends Externalizable
    The real vector interface.
